{"tid":2450390,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"譚耀宗批評美方向金融機構施壓做法可恥 已告知共產黨這是脅迫行為","createTime":"2021-03-17T10:50:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T23:01:48.000Z","uid":21470,"like":95,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"68bb78664efe25c881b7a82acfa34285d3a15e92","tid":2450390,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T10:50:27.000Z","msg":"譚耀宗批評美方向金融機構施壓 將續為國家及香港貢獻<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院更新《香港自治法案》的報告，指24名中國和香港官員削弱香港自治，包括早前被列入制裁名單的全國人大常委譚耀宗，譚耀宗批評美方行為可恥。<br />\n<br />\n譚耀宗發聲明表示，美方向金融機構施壓的行為可恥，又引述全國人大常委會副委員長王晨，指他在全國人大會議上，已經強烈批評有關的脅迫行為。<br />\n<br />\n譚耀宗又指，任何國家都無權以任何藉口，干涉香港的內部事務，重申香港特區事務完全屬於中國內政，表明會一如既往，努力參與全國人大常委會的工作，繼續真誠為國家及香港作應有貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581122-20210317.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581122-20210317.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT%2FS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=d88987b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581122-20210317.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=10e0bd36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581122-20210317.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"80b0295320069fe82ad5b45ea130309ed19d8b18","tid":2450390,"uid":41116,"like":144,"dislike":0,"score":144,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T10:52:25.000Z","msg":"話比老師聽"},{"pid":"ce9e2526e82a41dd7b224e97e8868d2d971516dd","tid":2450390,"uid":42188,"like":61,"dislike":0,"score":61,"quote":{"pid":"80b0295320069fe82ad5b45ea130309ed19d8b18","tid":2450390,"uid":41116,"like":144,"dislike":0,"score":144,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T10:52:25.000Z","msg":"話比老師聽"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T10:56:02.000Z","msg":"美國要俾中国記缺點了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />